gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Thunder 112, Magic 100
gameRecap.excerpt: Oklahoma City defeated Orlando, 112-100, as they win their fourth consecutive game and improve to 27-11 on the year. Shai Gilgeous-Alexander led the Thunder with 37 points, six rebounds, and seven assists as Jalen Williams (16 points, six rebounds) and Chet Holmgren (15 points, eight rebounds, two blocks) added 31 points. Paolo Banchero led Orlando with 20 points, nine rebounds, and eight assists. The Magic move to 21-18 on the year.
